1010502.name: Promise to A Long Lost Friend

1011114.name: A Symphony of Wind and Water

1011235.name: You, In a Sea of People

1011612.name: The Dark Side of the Akishika Family

1031900.name: Main - 01: Heartlock
1031900.tips: In a sequestered ward, the girl, unable to leave her room, can only gaze at the petals falling in the courtyard and at an unreachable tomorrow.

1031901.name: Main - 03: Blunt Sword
1031901.tips: The unarmed knight stands alone in front of the broken monument, surrounded by ghosts.

1031902.name: Main - 06: Both Friend and Foe
1031902.tips: The fool dances a distant dance with a cruel smile visible through a crack in their mask.

1031903.name: Main - 08: Belligerent
1031903.tips: The lights have come on again. Despite having lost their audience, the actor continues to sing to themselves in what is another curtain call.

1031904.name: Main - 14: Agent in Action
1031904.tips: The low hum of insects can be heard in the quiet corners touched by the moonlight, echoing among the flowers.

1031905.name: Main - 19: Urgent Assistance
1031905.tips: Courage is not always as hard as steel. Sheep's wool can also withstand the bite of sharp teeth.

1031906.name: Main - 24: The Other Side
1031906.tips: "In the dreamer's dream, the person who is dreamed of wakes up."

1031907.name: Main - 28: Shadowy Tide
1031907.tips: The sun is setting. Swarms of shadows loom and flood the outpost like a tide, threatening the city gates.

1031908.name: Main - 30: The Future Is Here Again
1031908.tips: In the nightmare of tomorrow, I have caught a glimpse of your hideous shape—and in the fragments of yesterday, I have found a reason to wake up.

1031909.name: Main - 35: Fantasy From the Past
1031909.tips: "The six armies had agreed to stay put with their horses, recalling the time when Xuanzong and Concubine Yang mocked the Cowherd and the Weaver Girl for only meeting once a year during the Qixi Festival."

1031910.name: Main - 40: The Search
1031910.tips: The final act, a return to the original starting point. Hidden in the upcoming coda are clues to the overture.

1031911.name: Main - 42: Winners and Losers
1031911.tips: The naughty child forms a battle formation with their toys, and the evil king's army surrounds the shepherdess who's entered the battle formation. The naughty child breaks out laughing.

1031912.name: Main - 46: The Great Cleanup
1031912.tips: The two hearts beat in sync for a moment amidst the great clamor. A killer fire is about to break out under the chaotic stage.

1031913.name: Main - 48: Hunting While Mad
1031913.tips: The mad puppet, wearing an empty crown, raises the broken sword at the princess who has lost her homeland.

1031928.name: Main - 02: Post-dream Emptiness
1031928.tips: Sometimes, reality is more cruel than nightmares. A strange space and imminent danger, with the dream still stinging somewhat. But there is no time to pause for the sword held in the hand.

1031929.name: Main - 04: Glimmer of Hope
1031929.tips: There seems to be no way out of the yawning purgatory. But before the knight falls into the hellfire, destiny casts a precious ray of light out of nowhere.

1031930.name: Main - 05: The One With No Name
1031930.tips: A path carved out by one's memories. The one who seeks home embarks on this path, only to find themselves on a cliff.

1031931.name: Main - 07: OPRIC
1031931.tips: The puzzle of the magic box is finally solved, but what emerges from the box only confounds. Where should one whose eyes are covered look for the answer?

1031932.name: Main - 09: Molander
1031932.tips: A name jumps out from the depths of memory. When a person who's been away from home throws herself into the embrace of an old dream, will she still find the ballad engraved on its wall?

1031933.name: Main - 10: The Year 2305
1031933.tips: Identity defines one's existence, and when one's identity is rejected by one's home, the world that is all around her suddenly becomes like a mirage.

1031934.name: Main - 11: Branch-off
1031934.tips: Time, wrongly reported again and again. An invisible hand moves the dial, though the calibrated hour hand is now pointing to a past that should not be repeated.

1031935.name: Main - 12: Hidden in the Moonlight
1031935.tips: Not only can light illuminate, it can also hide. Behind the quiet moonlight are secrets with the potential to upend everything.

1031936.name: Main - 13: Bird in a Cage
1031936.tips: The caged bird flies into the forever-sealed, gilded bars as its indifferent feeder looks on coldly.

1031937.name: Main - 15: Keys
1031937.tips: All stories of adventure start with an irresistible call. When the dusty gears of destiny start turning, the throbbing heart cannot help but go on exploration.

1031938.name: Main - 16: Lifting the Seal
1031938.tips: Strange new friends made as one goes back in time. The key to tomorrow has opened the door to one's childhood instead.

1031939.name: Main - 17: The Past
1031939.tips: Feelings that cannot be conveyed, and a starting point that cannot be reached.

1031940.name: Main - 18: Disruption
1031940.tips: A game disturbed by a passing child who has just blithely thrown a white piece onto the chessboard.

1031941.name: Main - 20: Simulated Nest
1031941.tips: When the steel nest is about to collapse, will the electronic bird save its man-made garden?

1031942.name: Main - 21: Chance and Effect
1031942.tips: A mistaken placement that is in line with the original plan of attack. Where will the clues, left unchecked, lead this time?

1031943.name: Main - 22: First Meeting, Again
1031943.tips: The past, future, and present have come together at this moment, and from the core of the intersection, out walks the person who cannot be forgotten.

1031944.name: Main - 23: Inquietude
1031944.tips: Different perspectives give different insights into the same story. Even the most familiar characters may have sides to them that have been hitherto unseen.

1031945.name: Main - 25: True Feelings
1031945.tips: One lie collides with another. Behind this clumsy mystery, there is an irrepressible true heart.

1031946.name: Main - 26: Reins on the Sun
1031946.tips: She's turned back to race against time to preempt future regret, and as she turns at an unremarkable corner, she grabs the reins of the setting sun.

1031947.name: Main - 27: Thread Interwoven
1031947.tips: Accidents. Tests. Coming-togethers. Creak, creak, creak goes the loom, and the disparate silk threads come together woven in a fashion completely unexpected.

1031948.name: Main - 29: Thorn in the Flesh
1031948.tips: The replay of the story appears to be getting out of control. The director has been forced to become a character in the play, and the phantom of the theater is climbing onto one's unguarded shoulders in every possible way.

1031949.name: Main - 31: Balance
1031949.tips: The phantom who is unable to sneak about in broad daylight is using chaos as their weight, and the scale is now tilting dangerously.

1031950.name: Main - 32: What I Wish to Say to Me
1031950.tips: I walk down that hallway at the end of the shadow of time, and in the mirror at the very end of that hallway, I embrace myself in my arms.

1031951.name: Main - 33: Meeting You Again
1031951.tips: History that has been written cannot be changed. However, if there's a chance for me to do it again, I'd like to meet you in a different way.

1031952.name: Main - 34: Visitor and Visitor
1031952.tips: Spectator or visitor, everyone has become an uninvited guest to each other.

1031953.name: Main - 36: Hope for the Future
1031953.tips: The dark clouds have dispersed and the gleaming moon has appeared. Faint and far away as it is, it continues to stubbornly shine.

1031954.name: Main - 37: Night Meeting
1031954.tips: I want to see you, even if it's only in my dreams. And even if there is no other choice, I am determined to see this through.

1031955.name: Main - 38: Wheels in Motion
1031955.tips: The battle lines here has been drawn, and the cherry blossoms on the other side have drifted to their destination. The tranquility of the night before is for the coming storm.

1031956.name: Main - 39: Mission From the President
1031956.tips: You hear nothing. You ask no questions. And interfere, you do not. Our mission? It's all a "secret."

1031957.name: Main - 41: Unwelcome Complication
1031957.tips: The mountain cat climbs over the wall, and the foundation of the Tower of Babel is about to appear before it. Right at this time, however, the puppet that's been behind the scenes for a long time is revealed.

1031958.name: Main - 43: Emergency Call
1031958.tips: An unexpected alarm bell has sounded. Where will the battle end when everyone's been gathered in the same trench?

1031959.name: Main - 44: High-risk Agreement
1031959.tips: Everything that's being done is for the final result. If one can get away with things unscathed, may as well try for more.

1031960.name: Main - 45: So Close, Yet So Far
1031960.tips: The knight rushes at the dancing jester with his sword as the playwright rushes to correct the out-of-control plot. Might there be an undercurrent they may not yet be aware of?

1031961.name: Main - 47: Out-of-balance Creation
1031961.tips: The puppet opens up its empty chest and fills its blackness up. But is it in jealousy or in pain?

1031914.name: Main - 53: Rehabilitation Training
1031914.tips: Same location, different space. Same equipment, different modes. The rehabilitation training is about to begin. The goal: a complete recovery.

1031915.name: Main - 56: So-called Resolve
1031915.tips: Insisting on a goal results in a resolute belief, and resolute beliefs collide into an unresolvable disagreement. How should the disagreement be handled?

1031916.name: Main - 60: Mistaken Understandings
1031916.tips: Mistaken understanding leads to erroneous behavior, which in turn leads to unexpected and adverse consequences. The slightest of deviation can lead to a major mistake.

1031917.name: Main - 64: Dancing With Dragons
1031917.tips: All games of adventure are about challenging unimaginable enemies. Faced with the impending threat, there is only one way, which is to draw the weapon and face the dragon.

1031918.name: Main - 66: Effective Sparring
1031918.tips: Tailormade training methods require the real-time adjustment of difficulty based on the subject's progress. Compared to the frequent adjustment of parameters, there is actually another, better way.

1031919.name: Main - 70: To the Peak
1031919.tips: The peak is known as such because it is higher than the average level. Is it easy to re-summit a peak you have already reached before?

1031920.name: Main - 73: Into the Unknown
1031920.tips: One will always encounter certainty if one is to follow your experience and plans. But when things are not what was expected and one steps into the unknown, what will one encounter?

1031921.name: Main - 76: The Living Must Go On
1031921.tips: Those who have passed lie in eternal rest, but the living must continue to move forward with their wishes and concerns for themselves, others, and their deceased companions, right to the very end.

1031922.name: Main - 80: Revisiting History
1031922.tips: Find value in the abandoned and seek out the truth from the forgotten: revisiting history is like picking up scraps and hoping for unexpected gains.

1031923.name: Main - 87: Hospitality
1031923.tips: The guardian's responsibilities must be fulfilled, even if they are taking some well-deserved rest.

1031924.name: Main - 89: Repeat to Exhaustion
1031924.tips: The end gives meaning to the means. However, if all of one's time were to be spent endlessly repeating a single means, the meaning will fray and the end will be forgotten.

1031925.name: Main - 91: Wishes, Yours and Mine
1031925.tips: If the outside world is not as wonderful as you've imagined, will realizing your wishes still bring happiness? But now that you've climbed over the high wall, try doing that which you wouldn't have dared to do before.

1031926.name: Main - 94: Forbidden Overtime
1031926.tips: The same task, but different takes. But in a team, sometimes someone has to take things into their own hands.

1031927.name: Main - 96: My Wish
1031927.tips: All that has been done has been in preparation for this moment. Remember the promise you've made with your friends and protect them until the last moment.

1031962.name: Main - 49: Dream Reunion
1031962.tips: A distant dream has brought back old friends who exist now only in memories. The questions directed at the dream only lead to answers from the self.

1031963.name: Main - 50: Paradox of Origin
1031963.tips: The dream is over, but life goes on. Once you open your eyes, you have to face both the things you want to see and those you don't.

1031964.name: Main - 51: Risk Mitigation
1031964.tips: A compromise for the time being is for a far greater goal. The road to truth has only one destined end.

1031965.name: Main - 52: A Brand New Goal
1031965.tips: Nothing beats seeing the truth for yourself, and the worried heart is comforted by a reunion. To return to the starting point is to set off again towards a new goal.

1031966.name: Main - 54: Differentiation and Discrimination
1031966.tips: To know someone is to call them by the right name. Two people, alike from head to toe. But do they act the same too?

1031967.name: Main - 55: Secret Interrogation
1031967.tips: How many new secrets have to be created to cover up an existing one? The best way to deal with leaks is to cut off the possibility of them happening entirely.

1031968.name: Main - 57: Proper SOP
1031968.tips: Non-standard or prescribed actions must be terminated in a timely manner. The core issue must be handled through the correct channels no matter what.

1031969.name: Main - 58: The Meaning of Existence
1031969.tips: It is a truth of our world that those who are ignorant do not know fear. Why is that so? What is it that can allow us to transcend fear and keep on moving forward?

1031970.name: Main - 59: Unexpected Visitor
1031970.tips: Forbidden thoughts aren't necessarily true forbidden zones. Where there is existence, there is always a path. An unexpected visitor or two is not that surprising.

1031971.name: Main - 61: A Peek
1031971.tips: The abnormality is hidden beneath the surface, and only by breaking through the surface can we get a glimpse of it. It is something that should never be seen.

1031972.name: Main - 62: Backup
1031972.tips: The facts are hidden in the fog, and the path of pursuit is paved with only fragmented information. One wrong inference, and one may tread down a dangerous path.

1031973.name: Main - 63: The New Store Clerk
1031973.tips: A calm and safe environment is destabilized by new elements. When new members join the team, the existing employees will inevitably experience some turbulence.

1031974.name: Main - 65: Unhelpful Thinking
1031974.tips: Avoid distractions when playing games. Only by focusing on the set goals will you be able to complete them with ease. Is it really necessary to think so much?

1031975.name: Main - 67: Absolute Trust
1031975.tips: To convey your faith across the yawning cold, there must be absolute trust.

1031976.name: Main - 68: Everything About You
1031976.tips: Time awakens longing, and longing breeds desire. Longing for your voice, your smile, your gaze, everything about you.

1031977.name: Main - 69: The Way Forward
1031977.tips: Life needs direction, and so does the mind. The direction of life is called a goal, and the direction of the mind is called a wish.

1031978.name: Main - 71: Finding the Right Method
1031978.tips: The physician has to tailor the treatment to the patient to get the results they want, and only through thorough analysis of the cause of the disease can a good treatment plan be drawn up.

1031979.name: Main - 72: Precision Medicine
1031979.tips: No matter how good a plan is, the only way to find out if it works is to apply it.

1031980.name: Main - 74: The Physician's Aspirations
1031980.tips: "Now that I'm part of the medical profession, I hereby pledge myself to it. The lives of my patients are my primary concern. I am responsible for all my patients, no matter who they are."

1031981.name: Main - 75: Gone But Not Forgotten
1031981.tips: No matter how beautiful one's appearance is, it will all eventually end with death with no physical trace left behind. But one can still be missed in the hearts of friends and thus not be forgotten.

1031982.name: Main - 77: Mutual Support
1031982.tips: The blazing sun overhead is unforgiving, and the road is long. Walking this road with companions who comfort you, support you, and wipe away your tears, however, can make the journey easier and allow us to overcome every difficulty as we move towards a better tomorrow.

1031983.name: Main - 78: Perceived Value
1031983.tips: What is poison to one may be honey to another. The value of an object often does not lie in its material or craftsmanship, but in the ideas and meanings it carries.

1031984.name: Main - 79: Plan of Last Resort
1031984.tips: The idea of using something simple and low-cost to solve a complex problem is a beautiful fantasy. When the problem cannot be solved, we can only rely on backup plans, even if the cost is much higher.

1031985.name: Main - 81: Impending Collapse
1031985.tips: The building is about to collapse, and chaos is beginning to emerge. The world is going off the rails. There's not much time left, and yet the wish remains unfulfilled. What does one do in these circumstances?

1031986.name: Main - 82: Always With a Smile
1031986.tips: Regardless of the ups and downs, or whatever losses or misunderstanding or disputes that have occurred, always face them with a smile. To be happy in this way is to be fortunate.

1031987.name: Main - 83: Cycles and Gyres
1031987.tips: The past is full of regrets, and there is always the impulse to make up for them one way or another. But are impulses and good intentions nearly enough?

1031988.name: Main - 84: Who Am I?
1031988.tips: The paradox has bared its fangs as it gnaws at the self-evident truth in one's cognition. If the ground on which we stand collapses, there will be an endless fall.

1031989.name: Main - 85: The Monster
1031989.tips: In the fall there are cries for help, cries that have become piercing screams. The feelings that cannot be communicated are regarded as abnormal and are rejected and isolated.

1031990.name: Main - 86: Gentle Wings
1031990.tips: The wings hold up the falling body, the feathers embracing the wounded heart. A gentle harbor one has sailed into. Take some rest before you go on.

1031991.name: Main - 88: Fixing a Broken Dream
1031991.tips: Even a beautiful wish shattered by misfortune and tainted by bitterness will surely bloom again as long as it is recast with sincerity.

1031992.name: Main - 90: We Two
1031992.tips: Looking at you is like looking myself. We share one beating heart along with the same fears.

1031993.name: Main - 92: As One
1031993.tips: We hold each other's hands, unwilling to lose each other. Together, we overcome confusion and fear, and our hearts beat together as one.

1031994.name: Main - 93: The Power I Have
1031994.tips: Your mind is no longer confused, and the power is in your hands. The wish is within grasp. For your own sake and everyone else's, it's now time to go and protect everything that you cherish.

1031995.name: Main - 95: Fiery Sun Overhead
1031995.tips: The appearance has been shattered and the world is falling apart.

1031996.name: Main - 97: A Long Way Home
1031996.tips: After traversing time and space and overcoming all the difficulties and obstacles, one can finally... go home.

1031997.name: Main - 98: A New Agreement
1031997.tips: It's been a long time. Let's talk to one another and forge a new promise between us. Despite this respite, a new storm has already appeared...

1011901.name: Ep 00
1011901.tips: Questions from within. No objection is allowed, no answers are expected, and no sway is made on the outcome.

1011902.name: Ep 01
1011902.tips: One person playing a game meant for four people, one person playing a story about seven people, and one person walking the paths of ten people.

1011903.name: Ep 02
1011903.tips: The interweaving of appearance and what lies beneath, of results unexpected and deserved. This is just the beginning.

1011904.name: Ep 03
1011904.tips: She asked her: How does one look ahead, persist, and have a heart that never changes?

1011905.name: Ep 04
1011905.tips: She answered for her: How do you take a step forward, travel the distance, and find a road that will never collapse?

1011906.name: Ep 05
1011906.tips: Before you wake up from your sweet dream, before the tears fall, do what you want to do—right now.

1011907.name: Ep 06
1011907.tips: The heart of a person who lacks courage is one that is empty. So she left her tears behind, jettisoned her anxiety, and started up her heart not with courage but a full spectrum of emotion.

1011908.name: Ep 07
1011908.tips: "In a place far, far away, there was a little person who happily trained with her sisters under the guidance of her mentor. She walked and she walked, but she never left that home."

1011909.name: Ep 08
1011909.tips: "In a place far, far away, there was a little person who trained really hard but she was all alone. She yelled and she yelled, but no one ever heard her."

1011910.name: Ep 09
1011910.tips: A gentle wish falling onto the dirt, a sweet wish hanging on the wall, and a beautiful wish remaining in the heart.

1011911.name: Ep 10
1011911.tips: Go forth and add some fun to your peaceful days, no matter if this fun be well-behaved and sweet or naughty and eccentric! All that is needed is to be happy. Just remember to be happy.

1011912.name: Ep 11
1011912.tips: Thus she prayed: May all illness and sorrows disappear from the world.

1011913.name: Ep 12
1011913.tips: Thus she prayed: May all good things and happiness come to us.

1011914.name: Ep 13
1011914.tips: The way can be a confusing one. However, the truth always awaits you at the end.

1011915.name: Ep 14
1011915.tips: May you find the meaning that belongs to you in this broken world.

1011916.name: Ec 01
1011916.tips:
Sep. 10th    On mission.
Sep. 11th    On mission.
Sep. 12th    On mission.

1011917.name: Ec 02
1011917.tips:
Sep. 10th    On mission.
Sep. 11th    On mission.
Sep. 12th    On mission.
Sep. 13th    Oh Ver, just how obsessed with going on missions are you? Is this something you should be striving for? Admin often says that it's important to have work-life balance. It's time I give myself a day off!

1011918.name: Ec 03
1011918.tips:
Sep. 10th    On mission.
Sep. 11th    On mission.
Sep. 12th    On mission.
Sep. 13th    Oh Ver, just how obsessed with going on missions are you? Is this something you should be striving for? Admin often says that it's important to have work-life balance. It's time I give myself a day off!
Sep. 14th    On mission.

1020101.name: Nerve Center
1020101.tips: Zenki never runs out of zany ideas for battle. This time round, she's brought with her a "Scrap Metal Mind Controller..."

1020102.name: Wild Party
1020102.tips: A boring factory can also become a place for fun. In a game, that is—not in reality.

1020103.name: Kind and Friendly
1020103.tips: A friendly baby AGI Mecha with a sense of humor is standing in Zenki's way.

1020104.name: Product of Restlessness
1020104.tips: By disassembling her Access Key, Zenki has come up with yet another a new shooting trick.

1020105.name: Loot
1020105.tips: After the harvested AGI Mecha parts are sorted, a guard dog from Children of Iron appears.

1020106.name: King of Ink
1020106.tips: In order to escape from the factory with her loot, Zenki needs to defeat the high wall there.

1020201.name: Advance
1020201.tips: With the defeat of the security captain, Overture Squad has further penetrated the line of AGI Mechas.

1020202.name: Broken AGI Mechas
1020202.tips: Dangerous AGI Mechas have been put into action. The squad, however, will not back down.

1020203.name: An Obstinate Opponent
1020203.tips: The opponent is still putting up a fierce fight. This is taking way too much time.

1020204.name: A Huge Army
1020204.tips: Acting on Jolin's intel, Ver, Shu, and Osiris rush to the lower levels of the factory.

1020205.name: The Last Line
1020205.tips: They are almost at their destination. However, they continue to face a stream of opponents.

1020206.name: Battle Dance Duo
1020206.tips: The trio finally beat the guards of the Children of Iron and come face to face with Olheim and Zero One.

1020301.name: On the Way
1020301.tips: Ver, Osiris, and Shu get onto the elevator on their way to regroup with Baldr.

1020302.name: About Tutorials
1020302.tips: Learning happens all the time, even during combat. Maybe her very presence here will serve as teaching material for the rookies.

1020303.name: How to Grow
1020303.tips: The trio continue on their way. Ver and Osiris try to imagine what Shu was like when she was still a rookie.

1020304.name: The Very Beginning
1020304.tips: In the midst of battle, Shu recalls her days as a rookie.

1020305.name: To Maturity
1020305.tips: Shu encourages Ver and Osiris, telling them one day they will become even better Modifiers.

1020306.name: Teacher and Student
1020306.tips: The trio arrive outside the control room and work together to defeat the enemy. They then head over to Baldr to help.

1020401.name: The Best Version of You
1020401.tips: Vidar and Leviathan set out for the factory in Neuhansa upon receiving their mission.

1020402.name: You're Here With Me
1020402.tips: Vidar leads Leviathan as they deal with the fleeing AGI Mechas they encounter along the way.

1020403.name: Your Protection
1020403.tips: On the road, Leviathan is in a good mood while Vidar keeps her eyes open for potential dangers around them.

1020404.name: You and More
1020404.tips: The two come to the perimeter of the factory, where they meet up with Zenkibo and Apollo as planned.

1020405.name: Parents and Children
1020405.tips: The four of them then clear out the AGI Mechas on the factory perimeter.

1020406.name: Front and Sides
1020406.tips: The group work together against the enemy with Vidar at the forefront.

1020501.name: Defeat Them All
1020501.tips: Where Is Leviathan? Let's just take care of the enemy first!

1020502.name: Where Is Master?
1020502.tips: We were catching penguins together just a while ago... I must go look for her!

1020503.name: BANG! BANG! BANG!
1020503.tips: I see somebody who looks like Master. This had better not be a trick!

1020504.name: A Very Long Road
1020504.tips: I'm not afraid of anything, and I will find Master.

1020505.name: Not Lost
1020505.tips: Thankfully, Leviathan is inside the system and was never actually lost.

1020506.name: Two Sets of Memories
1020506.tips: I'll be able to see Master once I get rid of this bunch of enemies!

1020601.name: Searching Behind the Scenes
1020601.tips: After splitting up from Kuninotokotachi, Buzenbo and Mininja venture deep into the inner courtyard of the Miyahebi compound to conduct their search.

1020602.name: Solo Venture
1020602.tips: Cut off from contact with Aether Gazer and with Izuru Masayoshi still missing, Buzenbo decides to enter the inner courtyard alone to continue the search.

1020603.name: Just What Was Wanted
1020603.tips: At the Miyahebis' inner courtyard, Buzenbo stumbles on a gathering of guards.

1020604.name: Hot Pursuit
1020604.tips: The fusion Visbane that can speak escapes right in front of Buzenbo, who goes off in hot pursuit in order not to lose her only clue.

1020605.name: Besieged
1020605.tips: After realizing that she's lost her target, Buzenbo finds herself deep in the inner courtyard, where she is surrounded by wandering Visbanes.

1020606.name: It Never Rains But It Pours
1020606.tips: After fighting her way out, Buzenbo goes off on a search of the Miyahebi house. However, right at the same moment, the figure of someone who has just been taught a lesson appears in front of her...

1020701.name: On the Back Foot
1020701.tips: While dealing with the loss of her left eye, Kuninotokotachi is surrounded by Visbanes again.

1020702.name: Following the Trail
1020702.tips: Concerned about Tsukuyomi and Buzenbo, Kuninotokotachi presses on despite her injuries to try and find them.

1020703.name: Feeling Unwelcome
1020703.tips: Kuninotokotachi is on Tsukuyomi's battle trail when a strange monk steps forward to stop her.

1020704.name: Truth or Illusion?
1020704.tips: Although she has fought off the Monk, Kuninotokotachi realizes that she's no longer at the gallery, but back in the front yard.

1020705.name: Mistaken Return
1020705.tips: Kuninotokotachi has been led by the Monk through an illusion to the front yard of the Miyahebi house. The continued fighting makes her injuries worse.

1020706.name: Doing One's Best
1020706.tips: Kuninotokotachi heads in the direction where the fused beasts are gathering in case there are people who need help, only to find a powerful enemy who is almost impossible to communicate with.

1020801.name: We All Have Our Job to Do
1020801.tips: Tsukuyomi and Buzenbo leave the Monk's illusory world and are determined to put an end to the madness and evil of the Miyahebi compound before it is too late.

1020802.name: Obstacle After Obstacle
1020802.tips: Buzenbo decides to continue the search for Izuru Masayoshi, and so the responsibility of destroying the experiment site falls on Tsukuyomi alone.

1020803.name: Swarm of Rats
1020803.tips: Tsukuyomi breaks past the Visbane defense and locates the entrance to the underground secret room. But naturally, an important location like this is heavily guarded.

1020804.name: In Search of the Origin
1020804.tips: After defeating the Polymerized Type Visbane, Tsukuyomi manages to enter the underground passage. However, there are more Visbanes blocking her way forward.

1020805.name: Base of Evil
1020805.tips: Tsukuyomi finally comes to the Miyahebis' underground secret room, where a part is still being tested. The evil here must be ended.

1020806.name: Roar of the Whale
1020806.tips: Tsukuyomi defeats the newly synthesized Visbanes and prepares to destroy the experiment site. A massive black whale suddenly appears, and a sworn guardian stands in her way.

1020901.name: Lightning
1020901.tips: Tsukuyomi summons Shinri in his haste to help Izuru Masayoshi.

1020902.name: Realm of Evil
1020902.tips: The Miyahebi compound is now swarming with Visbanes.

1020903.name: Powerful Enemy
1020903.tips: Faced with the enemy's obstruction, Tsukuyomi has no choice but to keep using Shinri.

1020904.name: Ghost Army
1020904.tips: Everyone is concerned by the appearance of large number of human-modified Visbanes.

1020905.name: Bloody Battle
1020905.tips: The lightning from Shinri may be the best salvation for these fallen warriors.

1020906.name: Deicide
1020906.tips: For the sake of hope and a promise, one man faces the evil god alone.

1021001.name: How Dare You!
1021001.tips: Why in the world is Hermes, who's rarely home, being hunted down by the Knights of Convallaria?

1021002.name: A Night Attack?
1021002.tips: Shockingly, a Visbane sits in disguise among those of the Society of Muses!

1021003.name: All Well Within Control
1021003.tips: Things just keep on happening, one after another. Looks like Hermes' vacation is over.

1021004.name: The Maid
1021004.tips: Due to poor communication, the dedicated maid prepares to "clean" Hermes.

1021005.name: Courier Time
1021005.tips: Olympia Express will send all who taint the sanctity of the temple far, far away!

1021006.name: Unintended Encounter
1021006.tips: Hermes ventures inside the temple to investigate, and runs into an unexpected opponent.

1021101.name: Counting Sheep
1021101.tips: Oneiroi, who is now in dreamland, decides to launch her very own sheep-counting campaign.

1021102.name: Dream in a Dream
1021102.tips: The tired Oneiroi begins to dream... while in a dream.

1021103.name: The Persistence of a Child
1021103.tips: In her dream, Oneiroi comes to the place where Athena once fought, and wiped out their existence.

1021105.name: Performance
1021105.tips: The not-so-pleasant dream continues, and Oneiroi is forced to go on stage.

1021106.name: Working With Your Hands
1021106.tips: Oneiroi finally locates the problem while in the dream and begins to think about how to solve it.
